<i>♪ Sweeter than wine ♪</i>

562
00:42:39,182 --> 00:42:41,352
<i>♪ Softer than a summer's night ♪</i>

563
00:42:42,977 --> 00:42:45,767
<i>♪ Everything I want, I have ♪</i>

564
00:42:47,523 --> 00:42:50,153
<i>♪ Whenever I hold you tight ♪</i>

565
00:42:52,528 --> 00:42:54,068
<i>♪ This magic moment... ♪</i>

566
00:42:54,906 --> 00:42:58,576
<i>The idea of pop music is not</i>
<i>to invent a new story,</i>

567
00:42:58,659 --> 00:43:03,039
<i>but to tell the same story again</i>
<i>in a new and interesting way.</i>

568
00:43:04,791 --> 00:43:06,421
<i>We don't buy new pop songs and say,</i>

569
00:43:06,501 --> 00:43:10,671
<i>"Oh, there's somebody singing about love,</i>
<i>nobody else has dared do that until now."</i>

570
00:43:12,173 --> 00:43:15,093
<i>People have been singing about love</i>
<i>for 500 years.</i>

571
00:43:15,176 --> 00:43:16,586
<i>♪ Why won't you dance with me? ♪</i>

572
00:43:19,055 --> 00:43:21,465
<i>And it's the idea of, like,</i>
<i>making it different,</i>

573
00:43:21,557 --> 00:43:24,437
<i>that you feel,</i>
<i>"Oh, I never actually until now,</i>

574
00:43:25,686 --> 00:43:27,896
<i>nobody has ever gotten it right."</i>

575
00:43:27,980 --> 00:43:29,360
<i>♪ This magic moment ♪</i>

576
00:43:32,527 --> 00:43:35,737
<i>♪ So different and so new ♪</i>

577
00:43:35,822 --> 00:43:37,742
<i>♪ Was like any other... ♪</i>

578
00:43:38,407 --> 00:43:41,867
<i>I love the idea of bringing</i>
<i>these familiar scenes back in,</i>

579
00:43:42,870 --> 00:43:45,580
<i>but just making them</i>
<i>appear to be totally different.</i>

580
00:43:45,665 --> 00:43:46,995
<i>New and true.</i>

581
00:43:49,377 --> 00:43:52,457
<i>♪ You know it took me by surprise ♪</i>

582
00:43:53,297 --> 00:43:56,627
<i>♪ I knew that you felt it too ♪</i>

583
00:43:57,677 --> 00:43:58,587
<i>♪ Mmm ♪</i>

584
00:43:58,678 --> 00:44:01,258
<i>♪ By the look in your eyes ♪</i>

585
00:44:02,306 --> 00:44:04,426
<i>♪ Sweeter than wine ♪</i>

586
00:44:05,476 --> 00:44:06,936
[Christoph] <i>In the best moments,</i>

587
00:44:07,019 --> 00:44:10,109
<i>what happens</i>
<i>is that design celebrates the world.</i>

588
00:44:11,691 --> 00:44:14,901
<i>♪ Everything I want, I have ♪</i>

589
00:44:14,986 --> 00:44:18,236
[Christoph] <i>When I look at a piece of art</i>
<i>that references my fears,</i>

590
00:44:18,322 --> 00:44:19,952
<i>my anxieties, my hopes,</i>

591
00:44:21,242 --> 00:44:26,502
<i>and I can say, "There was this one drawing</i>
<i>that made me realize that I'm alive</i>

592
00:44:26,581 --> 00:44:29,171
<i>or that I love other people</i>
<i>or that I'm afraid."</i>

593
00:44:30,209 --> 00:44:32,379
<i>♪ Sweeter than wine ♪</i>

594
00:44:34,589 --> 00:44:37,469
<i>♪ Softer than a summer's night ♪</i>

595
00:44:42,638 --> 00:44:43,718
<i>♪ So please ♪</i>

596
00:44:46,559 --> 00:44:47,939
<i>♪ Baby ♪</i>

597
00:44:48,352 --> 00:44:49,772
<i>♪ So please ♪</i>

598
00:44:51,522 --> 00:44:54,112
<i>♪ Save the last dance for me ♪</i>

599
00:44:58,404 --> 00:45:00,784
[clock ticking]

600
00:45:02,658 --> 00:45:05,538
[Christoph] <i>My goal is to speak visuals...</i>

601
00:45:06,078 --> 00:45:08,458
<i>like a pianist speaks piano.</i>

602
00:45:09,415 --> 00:45:11,245
<i>And like somebody controls the keys</i>

603
00:45:11,334 --> 00:45:13,964
<i>and can convey different ideas,</i>
<i>different emotions,</i>

604
00:45:14,045 --> 00:45:15,495
<i>through that language.</i>

605
00:45:22,053 --> 00:45:28,063
<i>I have to constantly battle to try to</i>
<i>kind of refine the act of speaking.</i>

606
00:45:30,937 --> 00:45:34,317
<i>Taking the world and putting it</i>
<i>into images and conveying them.</i>

607
00:45:36,317 --> 00:45:38,647
<i>And for that,</i>
<i>I have to constantly produce.</i>

608
00:45:39,528 --> 00:45:42,278
<i>It's not done,</i>
<i>because the whole idea of being done</i>

609
00:45:42,365 --> 00:45:45,235
<i>is kind of the opposite</i>
<i>of what I'm trying to achieve.</i>

610
00:45:45,326 --> 00:45:46,656
[instrumental music playing]

611
00:45:46,744 --> 00:45:48,294
<i>Gute Nacht.</i>

